@startuml
[Markdown Engine] as Engine
[Diagram Renderer] as KDR
component "PlantUML Runtime" as PlantUML
interface "SVG output" as SVG
database "Runtime Cache" as Cache

Engine --> KDR : render plantuml block
KDR ..> PlantUML : SourceStringReader
KDR --> SVG
KDR --> Cache : checksum
note right of KDR
  Returns SVG or raw code with warning.
end note
@enduml
